snippet.title: MEGA MAN X DiVE Offline - Character Introduction Trailer
snippet.description:
MEGA MAN X DiVE Offline is available now on Steam, iOS, and Android! Enjoy fast-paced side-scrolling action that lets you choose from more than 100 iconic playable characters from Mega Man Legends, Mega Man Battle Network, Mega Man Star Force, and other series in the Mega Man franchise. Get ready to DiVE into the Deep Log and embark on a mission to save the world of Mega Man X!

Official Site: https://www.capcom-games.com/megaman/xdive-offline/en-us/
